%% ModelMesh Serving - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.25/modelmesh-serving.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant MMesh as ModelMesh Sidecar<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant MMesh2 as ModelMesh (other pod)<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Runtime Container<br/>gRPC (UDS/TCP)
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP HTTP
    participant Puller as Puller Sidecar<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: Model Inference (REST via OAuth)
    Client->>OAuthProxy: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTPS 8443, TLS, OAuth Token
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthProxy: Validate OAuth token<br/>against OpenShift
    OAuthProxy->>RESTProxy: HTTP 8008<br/>plaintext (localhost)
    RESTProxy->>MMesh: gRPC 8033<br/>Optional TLS (localhost)
    MMesh->>etcd: Lookup model placement<br/>HTTP 2379, password auth
    etcd-->>MMesh: Model location info
    alt Model on this pod
        MMesh->>Runtime: gRPC inference<br/>UDS or TCP, plaintext
        Runtime-->>MMesh: Prediction result
    else Model on another pod
        MMesh->>MMesh2: Forward request<br/>gRPC 8080, plaintext
        MMesh2->>Runtime: gRPC inference
        Runtime-->>MMesh2: Prediction result
        MMesh2-->>MMesh: Prediction result
    end
    MMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
    RESTProxy-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP response
    OAuthProxy-->>Client: HTTPS JSON response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: Model Inference (gRPC direct)
    Client->>MMesh: gRPC 8033<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    MMesh->>etcd: Lookup model placement<br/>HTTP 2379, password auth
    etcd-->>MMesh: Model location
    MMesh->>Runtime: gRPC inference<br/>plaintext
    Runtime-->>MMesh: Prediction result
    MMesh-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over K8sAPI,Storage: Flow 3: Model Registration
    K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Predictor/InferenceService created
    Note right of K8sAPI: PredictorReconciler watches
    K8sAPI-->>MMesh: Controller calls SetVModel<br/>gRPC 8033, Optional TLS
    MMesh->>etcd: Store vModel mapping<br/>HTTP 2379, password auth
    MMesh->>Puller: Download model<br/>gRPC 8086, plaintext
    Puller->>Storage: Fetch model artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Storage credentials
    Storage-->>Puller: Model artifacts
    Puller-->>MMesh: Model ready
    MMesh->>Runtime: Load model

    Note over K8sAPI,Storage: Flow 4: Runtime Deployment Creation
    K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: ServingRuntime CR created
    Note right of K8sAPI: ServingRuntimeReconciler watches
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>(mm + runtime + puller + oauth-proxy + rest-proxy)
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAPI: Create/update etcd Secret<br/>for namespace coordination
